videos.description: Virginia Tech's Justin Robinson pushes the ball up the court off the turnover and finds Ahmed Hill of the last-second layup before the half.
videos.headline: Hill hits buzzer-beater before half

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Khalid Moore gets fed on the nice cut to the basket and hits Abdoulaye Gueye for the open dunk.
videos.headline: Great passing leads to Gueye dunk
